      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Ms. Abernathy was a teacher for 20 years in the Burrall Sunday School Bible Class for Young Women, Calvary Baptist Church, Washington, D.C. where her husband, Rev. Dr. William S. Abernathy, was pastor.  Died 1965.</abstract>
